PN,42802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1779117069
OL,3,CSeismic election results in the North
OL,4,CEast plus - are we heading for a new
OL,5,CPM?
OL,7,FCllr Paul Mackings told Tom Sheldrick
OL,8,Fon Around the House that he wants to
OL,9,Ftackle South Tyneside Council's
OL,10,Ffinances, along with antisocial
OL,11,Fbehaviour and improving economic
OL,12,Fgrowth.
OL,14,FHe accepted that the new Reform UK
OL,15,Fcouncillors have little or no
OL,16,Fexperience of serving on a local
OL,17,Fauthority, but believes that can be a
OL,18,Fgood thing.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1779117069
OL,3,CSeismic election results in the North
OL,4,CEast plus - are we heading for a new
OL,5,CPM?
OL,7,FHe said: "I've met all of the people
OL,8,Fwho are new councillors and they come
OL,9,Ffrom different walks of life and their
OL,10,Fexperience, your know - from
OL,11,Fhealthcare to children's services to
OL,12,Fpolice, businesses."
OL,14,FCllr Mackings believes his business
OL,15,Fbackground will help him make the
OL,16,Fright decisions for South Tyneside.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
