FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1779117069
OL,3,CSeismic election results in the North
OL,4,CEast plus - are we heading for a new
OL,5,CPM?
OL,7,F"I'm not a career politician but in
OL,8,Fterms of running businesses, I know
OL,9,Fhow to run a tight ship, look at
OL,10,Fcosts, look at wastage, look at all
OL,11,Fthe things we'd need to look at to
OL,12,Fimprove the financial situation - but
OL,13,Falso how to manage people and get the
OL,14,Fbest out of people, they're my skills
OL,15,FI think," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
